            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "thin 64Zn target (550 mu-g/cm2 and 1000 mug/cm2 for",
                "the 10,11Be  beams,respectively)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 6 dE (~ 50 mu-m thick) - E (~ 1500 mu-m",
                " thick) Si telescopes, each one with a surface of",
                "50x50mm2). The dE stage consists of a Double sided",
                "Silicon Strip Detector segmented in 16+16 strips,",
                "allowing a 256 detector pixels for each detector,",
                "and the E stage consists of a Single Pad detector"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The light charged particles  emitted",
                "in the reaction have been detected by an array of",
                "5 dE (~ 10 mu-m  thick) - E (~  150 mu-m thick) Si",
                "detector telescopes each consisting of a Surface",
                "Barrier  detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The experimental data were analyzed within the optical",
                "framework and along with the optical potential",
                "parameters, the total reaction cross section were",
                "extracted."
              ]
            }
